{
  "id": "S2P05K63",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "CUSTOM KEY ASSIGNMENT",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "After hitting Enter, the EDIT KEY DEFINITION panel is displayed,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "which allows you to change the label and value of the key.  For"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "example, after hitting Ctrl-Numeric 5 and hitting Enter, the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "following panel is displayed:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "KEY NAME  ==> Ctrl CUSTOM-00143"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "KEY VALUE ==>"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "On this panel, KEY NAME represents the \"label\" that is will"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "identify this key from the other custom keys.  The label is"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "purely informational field, and its contents can contain"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "anything that will help you identify the key later.  Typically,"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "you would want the label to correspond to whatever is printed"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "on the key.  For that reason, we change the label to:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "KEY NAME  ==> Ctrl Numeric-5"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
